analysis.overnightSummary: VPD averaged 1.53 kPa, nearly triple the 0.6 kPa seedling target, with only 3% time in optimal range. Environment shows classic dry basement pattern with VPD dropping overnight as humidity rises, then spiking during day cycle.
issuesDetected: VPD consistently too high (avg 1.53 vs target 0.6)

Day cycle showing severe drying (2.0+ kPa) likely from lights
positives: Humidifier did achieve brief periods in target range (10:00-10:30 AM)
System is responsive to environmental changes
